ViewObject.SQLQuery: /* Formatted on 3/18/2020 12:11:49 PM (QP5 v5.256.13226.35510) */ SELECT MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_NO, (SELECT customer_name FROM ar_customers ac WHERE ac.CUSTOMER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.Buyer_Id) buyer, MnjMfgPrecostingH.SEASON, MnjMfgPrecostingH.BRAND, --MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO, commented by Mr. Sakibul Islam for fetching current_style_no on 18.Mar.2020 /** Case statement added by Mr. Sakibul Islam for fetching current_style_no on 18.Mar.2020 **/ CASE WHEN (SELECT DECODE (StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS, 'Style Name', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME, 'Style Number', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 ) IS NULL THEN MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO WHEN (SELECT DECODE (StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS, 'Style Name', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME, 'Style Number', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 ) IS NOT NULL THEN (SELECT DECODE (StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS, 'Style Name', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME, 'Style Number', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 ) END STYLE_NO, MnjMfgPrecostingH.FIT, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ORDER_QTY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_ID, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ORDER_PROJECTION_NO, MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID, MnjMfgPrecostingH.DROP_PERIOD, MnjMfgPrecostingH.END_USER, (SELECT LISTAGG (COLOUR, ' , ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY HEADER_ID) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT L.COLOUR, L.HEADER_ID FROM MNJ_MFG_PRECOSTING_L L WHERE L.HEADER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_ID)) COLOUR, (SELECT LISTAGG (WASH_NAME, ' , ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY HEADER_ID) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT L.WASH_NAME, L.HEADER_ID FROM MNJ_MFG_PRECOSTING_L L WHERE L.HEADER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_ID)) WASH_N, MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NAME, (SELECT DECODE (StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS, 'Style Name', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME, 'Style Number', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NAME AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID) Current_Style_Name, MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NAME_NEW, (SELECT DECODE (StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS, 'Style Name', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME, 'Style Number', StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID) Current_Style_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ITEM_DESCRIPTION, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COLOUR_WASH, MnjMfgPrecostingH.OTHER_CHARGES, MnjMfgPrecostingH.LAB_TEST_CHARGES, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PRINT, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COMMISSION, MnjMfgPrecostingH.SMS_QTY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COSTING_MOU, MnjMfgPrecostingH.FABRIC_FINANCE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRIM_FINANCE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.WASH_FINANCE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PRODUCTION_UNIT, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CM_MERCHANDISER, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CREATED_BY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.LAST_UPDATED_BY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CREATION_DATE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.LAST_UPDATED_DATE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PROD_PER_LINE_PER_H, MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRANSFER_STATUS, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COSTING_STATUS, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Status, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Gm_Approval, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Md_Approval, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Cm_Merchandiser_d, NULL BUYER_CRITERIA, DECODE (MnjMfgPrecostingH.Gm_Approval, 'I', 'Inprocess', 'Y', 'Approved', 'Incomplete') gm_status, DECODE (MnjMfgPrecostingH.Md_Approval, 'I', 'Inprocess', 'Y', 'Approved', 'Incomplete') md_status, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Sample_Doc_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Version_Date, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Version_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Poc_Type, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Prod_Style_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_EFFICIENCY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.SMV, MnjMfgPrecostingH.SAM, MnjMfgPrecostingH.FACTORY_AVG_EF, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COST_NEW, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PROD_COST_LINE_PER_H, MnjMfgPrecostingH.AGENCY_COMMISSION, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CM_CALCULATION, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ITEM_PURCHASE_TYPE, -- (SELECT COUNT (1) -- FROM MNJ_FILE_UPD_DWN ff -- WHERE ff.file_id = 'PC' || MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_NO) -- ATTACHEMNT,--Commented by Mr. Sakibul Islam on 18.Mar.2020 MnjMfgPrecostingH.DIVISION FROM MNJ_MFG_PRECOSTING_H MnjMfgPrecostingH WHERE MnjMfgPrecostingH.Version_No = ( SELECT MAX (Version_No) FROM MNJ_MFG_PRECOSTING_H h2 WHERE h2.header_no = MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_NO GROUP BY h2.header_no) AND MnjMfgPrecostingH.Buyer_Id IN (SELECT V.BUYER_ID FROM MNJ_USER_WISE_BUYERS_DET_V v WHERE CASE WHEN 1607 = :p_userId THEN '1607' ELSE V.USER_ID END = :p_userId) AND ( MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRANSFER_STATUS = 'Y' OR MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRANSFER_STATUS = 'N') ORDER BY MnjMfgPrecostingH.Header_Id DESC
